      "body" : "Given that the only work-related RPC output is already measured in difficulty, perhaps use the same unit?\r\n\r\nAnother related and useful unit for transactions and blocks, is depth measured in \"equivalent current blocks\", namely the difference between chainwork of the tx/block under consideration and the chainwork of the tip, divided by the chainwork of the tip block.",
